ascii tab by: Lann <sylenz@hotmail.com>
This is a nice version of this romantic piece best enjoyed with a classical guitar. The timing bars should be used only as a guide, and I didn't include any indication of the duration of notes (sorry...). However, after getting the feel of the song, you'll know the best place and duration for each note...
Guitar pro tablature by: Tang (fot@tm.net.my)
I import the ascii tab file by Lann (big thx to him for this wonderful tab!), and edit the duration by myself (hopefully most of it is correct), and also edit the dynamics, so that you can get the feel of this song. This song is really nice to play and hear so enjoy! :)
